flowchart TB
    User["User Device"]-->|Interacts|App
    
    App["Android App"]-->|Auth|Auth
    App-->|Store/Retrieve Data|Firestore
    App-->|Store Metadata|Firestore
    App-->|Store/Retrieve Docs|Storage
    App-->|Verify PAN|PAN
    App-->|Start BRE Process|Camunda
    App-->|Send Events|Functions
    
    Auth["Firebase Auth"]
    Firestore["Firestore DB"]
    Storage["Firebase Storage"]
    Functions["Firebase Cloud Functions"]
    
    Camunda["Camunda Engine"]-->|Request Bureau Data|Appwrite
    Camunda-->|Single-Pass Task|BRE
    BRE["Python BRE Worker"]-->|Decision Result|Camunda
    Camunda-->|Update Status|Firestore
    
    Functions-->|Monitor Inactivity|Firestore
    Functions-->|Drop-off Analysis|LLM
    Functions-->|Send Drop-off Summary|Email
    Functions-->|Update Status|Firestore
    
    Appwrite["Appwrite Bureau DB"]
    LLM["LLM Service (Gemini/OpenAI)"]
    Email["Email Service (Brevo)"]
    PAN["PAN Verification API"]
